Service Details: - Develops and implements high-impact projects that address economic, social and environmental issues and contribute to the development of our small business economies- Provides support and immediate aid to local food banks by running projects designed to collect much needed donations and funds- Helps to raise awareness for local agriculture and supports farmers by creating an off-season market- Operates from the four campuses of Okanagan College:  Kelowna, Vernon, Penticton, and Salmon Arm
